{"tid":339981,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手]點樣用匯豐e-bank轉帳去恆生信用卡戶口?","createTime":"2017-07-29T13:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T19:43:30.000Z","uid":90587,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"743aa18172ab51cca169dcb5082c8d78580f5bf1","tid":339981,"uid":90587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"我一向係用開匯豐銀行<br />\n今日諗住用匯豐e-bank過數比恆生信用卡戶口<br />\n先發覺匯豐e-bank過數只可以輸入12位戶口數字<br />\n但恆生信用卡係16位數字<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/214220_de74c88fa3c485cf37d35f1b33155546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F214220_de74c88fa3c485cf37d35f1b33155546.jpg&h=6b0dce53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下點樣係網上交恆生信用卡卡數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c718b1ad519df8547905dd24c428f2d820284b","tid":339981,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"唔解唔用pps？<br />\n去ok禁幾個制就開到"},{"pid":"06e2b9d4dea7ee485ff7680cdfae35509073ae8b","tid":339981,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"pps la"},{"pid":"cbbe75a6898125daa89004e6f57fd7604e3480eb","tid":339981,"uid":105856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"PPS"},{"pid":"0c011dfaa339755abeb98576015b9ae758070b37","tid":339981,"uid":26037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"唔係過數<br />\n要用交單嗰到"},{"pid":"570229d1a164d16067a5af2dbd6aeb73de0125ae","tid":339981,"uid":60156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一向係用開匯豐銀行<br />\n今日諗住用匯豐e-bank過數比恆生信用卡戶口<br />\n先發覺匯豐e-bank過數只可以輸入12位戶口數字<br />\n但恆生信用卡係16位數字<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/214220_de74c88fa3c485cf37d35f1b33155546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F214220_de74c88fa3c485cf37d35f1b33155546.jpg&h=6b0dce53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下點樣係網上交恆生信用卡卡數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無數多左，我今日網上問職員，佢話唔駛打銀行個編號，就算轉帳1蚊都唔駛比手續費"},{"pid":"b2ca4134f2e6c39666c00d184a6f1b196300f835","tid":339981,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"無得直接還咭數 先要轉去你恆生銀利戶口先"},{"pid":"5dbbdfda6b7c967ae81b4f28bd42fa8d12864d3b","tid":339981,"uid":9264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"Pps?而家咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fa49561b6674bdb13433926418cdac3f74346a","tid":339981,"uid":90587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無得直接還咭數 先要轉去你恆生銀利戶口先</blockquote><br />\n但我岩岩打左去恆生問<br />\n佢話我無恆生戶口都可以直接透過匯豐轉帳去信用卡號去交卡數<br />\n但匯豐個網又只可以輸入12個位<br />\n姐係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎再搞唔掂就要去整PPS"},{"pid":"4b8fc4242ad7aa30d7552b5f588c6a40597d5528","tid":339981,"uid":1014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以去hsbc atm入16位恆生acc"},{"pid":"4533094bc49b1020aa18d53dfd4a68969f88b5fa","tid":339981,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無得直接還咭數 先要轉去你恆生銀利戶口先</blockquote><br />\n但我岩岩打左去恆生問<br />\n佢話我無恆生戶口都可以直接透過匯豐轉帳去信用卡號去交卡數<br />\n但匯豐個網又只可以輸入12個位<br />\n姐係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎再搞唔掂就要去整PPS</blockquote><br />\n咁你唔直接問埋佢點搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee441811d56f044bd7d5f44f28918c001c67db4","tid":339981,"uid":53420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係過數<br />\n要用交單嗰到</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db57ec564ce85d2e0a0e91c91ec59f9cc216d213","tid":339981,"uid":90587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係過數<br />\n要用交單嗰到</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無詳細D?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/230254_7d201ec2a29800ae55dacf022fd6eae5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F230254_7d201ec2a29800ae55dacf022fd6eae5.jpg&h=bc2be5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗你地講交單 應該係呢個界面?<br />\n但我係類別個到搵齊哂 都唔見有合適既選擇<br />\n得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/230423_43b602195e4466488359e78d97f6c2a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F230423_43b602195e4466488359e78d97f6c2a8.jpg&h=8797622d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀行類別個到又淨係得呢幾個選擇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/230439_1679e1cbb5523742cc752b79ed2f0319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F230439_1679e1cbb5523742cc752b79ed2f0319.jpg&h=9843916f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有用開hsbc e-bank交恆生信用卡數既<br />\n教教小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08b0d9eb4c97021ec005bd9e65ce134da3434ef","tid":339981,"uid":111163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"PPS一鍵輕鬆啦,乜銀行都得"},{"pid":"00b6edde7bda202d34ad9179f9cf9b958a220d9a","tid":339981,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:33:39.000Z","msg":"已經講到咁明都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e156c7148ae0abd9eed101e218488fc43ec2237f","tid":339981,"uid":90587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經講到咁明都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係講交單都唔知禁邊到<br />\n想問清楚D姐"},{"pid":"82ff4f08e7d51678200ed8ea4aec618a3241d38f","tid":339981,"uid":1014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T17:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經講到咁明都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁醒不如你講黎聽下點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次要找恆生卡數(極少用)都遇過咁既情況<br />\n搵左好耐，google完，記得有人話online係搞唔到<br />\n最後去atm搞算"},{"pid":"668220f320ddd1e8cf97bd434150dc0bb6876f8b","tid":339981,"uid":19925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T17:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已經講到咁明都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁醒不如你講黎聽下點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次要找恆生卡數(極少用)都遇過咁既情況<br />\n搵左好耐，google完，記得有人話online係搞唔到<br />\n最後去atm搞算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左pps冇得online 搞<br />\nhsbc 最多可以用atm account transfer"},{"pid":"3eab20ef670ff623415ea30365aafa37c11bed14","tid":339981,"uid":409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:01:41.000Z","msg":"之前問過佢d online cs話唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後用左pps 幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4368fd588d025d0348d69e